  "title": "Locum Healthcare Assistant (Flexi; choose your own slots) HMZT",
  "description": "<p>Our clients are hiring many Healthcare Assistants for a locum project. Candidates with experience in this area are welcome to apply!<br /><br />📍Location: Botanic Gardens</p><p>⏰ Working hours: AM shift - 8am - 9pm (1hr break unpaid) / PM shift - 8pm - 9am (1hr break unpaid)</p><p>💰Salary: $20/hr</p><p><br /><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist nurses in bedside care duties</li><li>Caring for elderly patients</li><li>Other work as assigned by supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Min 1 year of basic care/ HCA experience</li><li>Fully vaccinated for COVID, MMR and TDap</li><li>Valid BCLS</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates can apply now by sending your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>recruitmedical@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></a><strong></strong></p><p>OR call Natashya at <strong>6736 3280</strong> for more enquiries.</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Natashya Tasneem Thomas| Outsourcing Team | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p>",
